**Example 1: 获取历史搜索记录**



Input: 

```
tccli cwp DescribeSearchLogs --cli-unfold-argument ```

Output: 
```
{
    "Response": {
        "Data": [
            "yunjing",
            "106.55.40.250",
            "106.55.35.160"
        ],
        "RequestId": "498e4cab-e95d-430b-bc4c-f5821bb278d4"
    }
}
```
